These botanical waters are more than just refreshing — they’re naturally balancing, skin-loving, and beautifully aromatic.
</span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-e28e" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-18_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-19_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-20_ pf-heading-2-h2">What is Hydrosol ?<br></h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-22_ pf-heading-2-h3">GENTLE AROMATIC&nbsp;WATERS –&nbsp;HUMBLE, NATURAL, AND FULL OF FLOWER POWER.</h2></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-24_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-25_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-ad96b2a6-830f-4091-98f9-c059bbaadfa4"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Hydrosols are the gentle aromatic waters produced during the steam distillation of essential oils. Once thought of as a humble byproduct, they have&nbsp;since found their place as botanical treasures in natural skincare and wellness. More than just water with a scent, hydrosols contain the plant’s water-soluble compounds—like antioxidants, gentle acids, and trace minerals—that are lost in essential oil extraction. The result? A soothing, nutrient-rich mist that’s safe for sensitive skin and perfect for everyday rituals.</span></p><img alt="hydrosol plant resize.jpg__PID:f5d402c5-7fbf-4d0c-9f12-ea60de8c9067" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/hydrosol_plant_resize.jpg?v=1753864396&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.8620689655172413" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-28_" store="[object Object]"/></div></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-70da" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-29_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-30_ pf-heading-2-h2">How to use hydrosols</h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-32_ pf-heading-2-h3">HYDROSOLS ARE INCREDIBLY EASY TO USE — HERE ARE &nbsp;MANY WAYS TO ENJOY THEIR BENEFITS:<br> </h2><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-877a0a1d-d659-4b48-befd-1080336f38cc"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Hydrosols deliver the light, natural essence of plants in their most approachable form—gentle, aromatic, and easy to use every day. Unlike essential oils, they offer subtle support without overwhelming the senses. From freshening your skin to uplifting your mood or adding calming energy to your space, these pure floral waters fit effortlessly into your routine. Discover how a simple mist can become your go-to ritual for care, clarity, and connection.</span></p><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-37_"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-38_"><img alt="salina not orange.jpg__PID:f0c091af-2f17-49df-8b80-f7010a8feed7" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/salina_not_orange.jpg?v=1754377979&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-39_" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-40_"><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-41_ pf-lg-hide" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-25d8bc70-da53-4fef-adf9-e23815fb1ffc"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Hydrosols are delightfully easy to use—natural, versatile, and ready to become part of your daily rituals. These aromatic waters offer gentle care for skin, mood, and space. Whether you’re misting your face, creating a calming room spray, or soothing delicate skin, there’s a hydrosol for it.<br>Explore all the beautiful ways you can invite plant-powered care into your day:</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:16px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eONOlN dawdJE pf-44_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-45_">Facial Toner – Spritz directly onto clean skin to hydrate and refresh</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-47_">Hair &amp; Scalp Freshener – Mist onto hair or scalp to hydrate and balance</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-49_">After Sun or Shaving – Calm and soothe sensitive or irritated areas</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-51_">Body Mist – Use after showering or throughout the day for light fragrance</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-53_">Linen or Pillow Spray – Mist your bed or clothing for a gentle botanical aroma</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-55_">Compress or Eye Mask – Soak a cloth in chilled hydrosol and apply to face or eyes</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-57_">Children &amp;&nbsp;Babies – Use gentle hydrosols (like chamomile or lavender) for calming care</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bStdFM fgfEIw pf-59_">DIY skincare &amp; home recipes – Mix hydrosols into homemade lotions, masks, or room sprays for a natural boost.</li></ul></div></div><a data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH hFkfQE pf-61_">VIEW HYDROSOLS</a></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-327c" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-63_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-64_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-65_ pf-heading-2-h2">The Art of&nbsp;Distillation Aromatic Waters</h2></div></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-3658" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-67_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-68_"><img alt="1080x1080 Rose blossoms.jpg__PID:b2330f09-36a9-4c82-86db-6fa8e5f3dd17" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_Rose_blossoms.jpg?v=1753873738&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-69_" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-70_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-71_ pf-heading-2-h3">WHERE WATER MEETS PLANT, AND SPIRIT BECOMES ESSENCE</h2><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-73_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0a5af732-7c89-487b-aa67-4d57feca3bbe"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">How It Works: At its core, steam distillation is a process that combines heat, water, and plant material. Steam rises through fresh petals, leaves, resins, or roots, unlocking their volatile compounds — the aromatic molecules responsible for the plant’s scent and therapeutic properties.<br></span></p></div></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-e743" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-76_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-77_"><img alt="1080x1080 distilation pics_.jpg__PID:a07de35e-9925-4b72-adc4-a9604cdd0aff" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080_distilation_pics_afd021f1-59d5-4916-b5a2-aa662652a1cd.jpg?v=1752051554&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-78_" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-79_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-80_ pf-heading-2-h3">STEAM DISTILLATION IS NOT JUST A PROCESS — IT'S A RITUAL OF TRANSFORMATION.</h2><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-82_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-a62768f0-ce01-4749-96a6-a6e9163acc48"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">As the steam cools, it condenses back into liquid form, now divided into two layers: the essential oil floats or sinks, depending on its density, capturing the plant’s most concentrated aromatic essence. </span></p></div></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-7ea6" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-gKlDTn jrBPeP pf-85_ pf-container-1"><div class="sc-jRGIGG bMuAgN pf-flex-section"><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-86_"><img alt="1080x1080-Sonjs spray_.jpg__PID:a3067dc8-e3c1-42e7-9d89-b5179dc84787" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/1080x1080-Sonjs_spray_357eeed4-cbbb-4322-a0a8-988dfd9a7cf4.jpg?v=1765458146&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image5" class="sc-fscnvs dncZrx pf-87_" store="[object Object]"/></div><div data-pf-type="FlexBlock" class="sc-fYXHKj TqaeK pf-88_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-89_ pf-heading-2-h3">ONE THAT TURNS THE SOUL OF THE PLANT INTO TWO SACRED GIFTS: ESSENTIAL OIL AND HYDROSOL.</h2><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-91_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-3a3a6d5c-f844-4eaf-af77-ac3a4e772ad3"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">The hydrosol — also known as floral water or hydrolate — is the delicately fragrant water that remains, infused with the water-soluble plant molecules and a hint of essential oil.Together, they are the twin spirits of the same distillation — one powerful and intense, the other gentle and nurturing.</span></p></div></div></section><se